  ('bookkeeper-moex-01917', 'bookkeeper', 'bookkeeper-moex-104-9a386a01', 'sub-bookkeeper-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '「陳太丘與友期行，期日中。過中不至，太丘舍去，去後乃至。」（《世說 新語．方正》） 文中所指稱的主詞，下列選項何者正確？', '["同", "同", "同", "三者皆同"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:03+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "55650f2180a5", "answer_pdf_sha1": "d5d38050b082", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "104170", "c": "602", "s": "1301", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "國文（作文與測驗）", "year": "104", "exam_name": "104年專技建築師、技師、第二次食品技師、不動產經紀人、記帳士考試", "original_question_number": 1, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "bookkeeper", "db_exam_id": "bookkeeper"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('bookkeeper-moex-01918', 'bookkeeper', 'bookkeeper-moex-104-9a386a01', 'sub-bookkeeper-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列各組「」內的文字，前後意義相同的是：', '["管仲，世所謂賢臣，然孔子「小」之／「小」不忍則亂大謀", "既相齊，食不「重」肉，妾不衣帛／君子不「重」則不威", "「爾」能為我迎得父還，吾將嫁汝／問君何能「爾」，心遠地自偏", "舉酒「屬」客，誦明月之詩，歌窈窕之章／駕一葉之扁舟，舉匏尊以相「屬」"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:03+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "55650f2180a5", "answer_pdf_sha1": "d5d38050b082", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "104170", "c": "602", "s": "1301", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "國文（作文與測驗）", "year": "104", "exam_name": "104年專技建築師、技師、第二次食品技師、不動產經紀人、記帳士考試", "original_question_number": 2, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "bookkeeper", "db_exam_id": "bookkeeper"}'::jsonb, NULL)
